 and radius from non-zero angular momentum affects the resonance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Apr 2018 16:23:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Sep 2018 17:47:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-18"}
