ng cyber resilience; mission modeling for cyber resilience; systems\nengineering for cyber resilience, and dynamic defense as a path toward cyber\nresilience.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Apr 2018 14:49:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-23"}
